'''[[死刑|死刑]]在[[阿聯酋|阿聯酋]]是一項法定的刑罰'''。

根据阿联酋的法律，多项罪行均可判处死刑，执行死刑的方式有[[行刑队枪决|行刑队枪决]]、[[绞刑|绞刑]]或[[石刑|石刑]]。<ref name="urlUAE: Death by stoning/ flogging | Amnesty International">{{cite web |url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/documents/MDE25/005/2006/en/ |title=UAE: Death by stoning/ flogging | Amnesty International |access-date=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2019-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826203335/https://www.amnesty.org/en/documents/MDE25/005/2006/en/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="urlTimeline of executions in UAE">{{cite web |url=https://gulfnews.com/going-out/society/timeline-of-executions-in-uae-1.2129533 |title=Timeline of executions in UAE |access-date=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2019-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105205028/https://gulfnews.com/going-out/society/timeline-of-executions-in-uae-1.2129533 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="urlWoman Sentenced To Death By Stoning In Abu Dhabi – Emirates Woman">{{cite web |url=http://emirateswoman.com/woman-sentenced-death-stoning-abu-dhabi/ |title=Woman Sentenced To Death By Stoning In Abu Dhabi – Emirates Woman |access-date=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2019-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629132701/https://emirateswoman.com/woman-sentenced-death-stoning-abu-dhabi/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="urlDuterte threatened deployment ban if OFW in UAE executed: Bello | BusinessWorld">{{cite web |url=https://www.bworldonline.com/duterte-threatened-deployment-ban-if-ofw-in-uae-executed-bello/ |title=Duterte threatened deployment ban if OFW in UAE executed: Bello | BusinessWorld |access-date=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2019-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105205026/https://www.bworldonline.com/duterte-threatened-deployment-ban-if-ofw-in-uae-executed-bello/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>现行法律允许对下列行为判处死刑:叛国、间谍、谋杀、成功煽动他人自杀、纵火致人死亡、不雅袭击致人死亡、叛教、强奸、情节严重的抢劫、恐怖主义、鸡奸、同性恋、贩毒<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.deathpenaltyworldwide.org/country-search-post.cfm?country=United+Arab+Emirates|title=The Death Penalty in United Arab Emirates|publisher=Death Penalty Worldwide|access-date=25 August 2017|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616140625/http://www.deathpenaltyworldwide.org/country-search-post.cfm?country=United%20Arab%20Emirates|dead-url=no}}</ref>和加入[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2016/2/15/uae-sentences-four-to-death-for-joining-is|title=UAE sentences four to death for joining IS|publisher=The New Arab|date=15 February 2016|access-date=6 December 2017|archive-date=2019-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105205028/https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2016/2/15/uae-sentences-four-to-death-for-joining-is|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2016/1/10/uae-sentences-jihadi-teenager-to-death-for-joining-is|title=UAE sentences 'jihadi teenager' to death for joining IS|publisher=The New Arab|date=10 January 2016|access-date=6 December 2017|archive-date=2019-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105205031/https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2016/1/10/uae-sentences-jihadi-teenager-to-death-for-joining-is|dead-url=no}}</ref>外国公民和阿联酋国民都有因犯罪被处决的案例。
==著名案例==
1995年，菲佣萨拉·巴拉巴甘引起了居住在阿联酋许多人的注意。据报道，她在她的雇主Al Ain的房子里谋杀了其雇主，尽管她一直坚称，她只是在他试图强奸她后自卫杀死了他。在阿联酋总统亲自介入后，巴拉巴甘被释放，但不得不支付赔偿金。但是，她被驱逐回她的国家，她留在该国的权利被取消。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.corpun.com/aeju9510.htm|title=Judicial caning, Arab Emirates, Oct 1995 - CORPUN ARCHIVE aeju9510|access-date=2020-12-29|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517011329/http://www.corpun.com/aeju9510.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年2月，拉希德·拉希迪被行刑队处决，2009年11月27日，他被控在一座清真寺的厕所内强奸并谋杀一名4岁的儿童莫萨·穆赫蒂尔。<ref>{{cite web |title=Child killer is executed by firing squad |url=https://www.thenational.ae/uae/child-killer-is-executed-by-firing-squad-1.423250 |website=The National |access-date=29 December 2019 |language=en |archive-date=2019-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191229062421/https://www.thenational.ae/uae/child-killer-is-executed-by-firing-squad-1.423250 |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{cite web |title=Dubai mosque murderer executed |url=https://gulfnews.com/uae/crime/dubai-mosque-murderer-executed-1.760146 |website=gulfnews.com |access-date=29 December 2019 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925065849/https://gulfnews.com/uae/crime/dubai-mosque-murderer-executed-1.760146 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年6月，联邦最高法院判处阿联酋女恐怖分子阿拉·巴德尔·哈什米死刑，罪名是谋杀伊比利亚·瑞安，并在一名埃及裔美国医生位于阿布扎比的家中植入“手工制作的炸弹”。该女子于2014年12月犯罪，于2015年7月13日凌晨被处决。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/911760/uae-woman-sentenced-to-death-for-killing-us-teacher/|title=UAE woman sentenced to death for killing US teacher|work=Express Tribune|date=29 June 2015|access-date=30 June 2015|archive-date=2017-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831043937/https://tribune.com.pk/story/911760/uae-woman-sentenced-to-death-for-killing-us-teacher/|dead-url=no}}</ref>这是囚犯在如此短的时间内被处决的唯一一次，也是为数不多的妇女被处决的案例之一。

